#########################
### ANOM package news ###
#########################

Please report weird or unexpected behavior to Philip Pallmann <p.pallmann@lancaster.ac.uk>

#########################

Version 1.0 (26 October 2025)

- Substantial refactoring, including S3 methods to separate by input class. 
- Removed internal function and moved functionality into general function
- Pass ellipsis parameter to ggplot, allowing full use of ggplot parameters
- Checked for visual back-compatibility with previous version.
- Added basic tests, checking for errors and warnings

#########################

Version 0.5 (10 April 2017)

- Added more flexibility for tweaking font sizes, line widths, colours, and background grid lines.
- Updated CITATION file.

#########################

Version 0.4.3 (15 February 2016)

- Included a CITATION file.
- Updated references in the help files and vignette.

#########################

Version 0.4.2 (13 October 2015)

- Fixed a bug with printp.

#########################

Version 0.4.1 (17 August 2015)

- Fixed a minor bug with the background color in ANOMgen.

#########################

Version 0.4 (12 August 2015)

- Added an option to switch between white or gray background.
- Moved the PDF vignette from folder inst/doc to vignettes.
- Added lme4 and nlme to Suggests.
- Changed e-mail of the package maintainer.

#########################

Version 0.3.1 (11 February 2014)

- Minor changes to the references.

#########################

Version 0.3 (19 November 2013)

- Added a vignette including a couple of worked examples. Type 'vignette("ANOM")' to check it out!